1) What is Python? What are the ways to install python in your pc?
	Python is an intepreted language that is easy to use with most easier syntax with added libraries to deal with.

	Python can be installed in 2 ways
	a) By downloading python software explicitly from python.org
	b) By installing anaconda software which includes python and in addition to other packages etc.

2) What are code environments? Types?
	Code Environment is a place in which one can write a piece of code, extract it and run the same to check its functionality.

	There are three types of Code Environments:
	1) Text Editors.
	2) IDLE(Integrated Development Environment for Python).
	3) Notebook Environment.
	